<div class="masthead">
  <%= title %>
  <div class="tagline">All you need is a few minutes, a printer, and a digital camera.</div>
</div>
<div class="left">
  <h2>How does this work?</h2>
  
  <p>We're putting together an interactive atlas of Bellingham, and we need your help. We want to show Google that Bellingham is the perfect mix of big city and small town, urban and rural &mdash; it’s <em>just right</em>. (Yes, we are going for a Goldilocks thing here.)</p>
  <p>We want you to help us put a face on it. We'll accept photo, video and text submissions for the next few weeks, and get everything plotted onto a map before the big day on March 26th.</p>
  <p>For more information on the community effort around bringing Google Fiber to Bellingham, check out <a href="http://www.googlefibertobellingham.com/">Bring Google Fiber to Bellingham</a>.</p>

  <h2>Step 1</h2>

  <p>Download our handy-dandy <%= link_to "<strong>PDF</strong>", "/google_sign.pdf" %> and print it out on any printer.</p>
  
  <h2>Step 2</h2>
  
  <p>Take a picture of you, your friends, or your dog holding the sign in front of your favorite Bellingham landmark or establishment. We'd particularly love to get photos with municipal landmarks, prominent local businesses, and all those beautifully quirky places that make this such a great place to live. Remember, we want Google to know that Bellingham is the <em>just right</em> location for Google Fiber because it has all the plus-sides of a smaller city with some of the best perks of a much larger city. It's not too much of anything, but just the right amount of everything &mdash; the just right middle ground for Google. Use your creativity to highlight what is just right about Bellingham. <!-- Can't think of anything? Visit our <%= link_to 'Wish List', '/wish-list' %>. --></p>
  
  <p>Got a video camera? Do a video version, upload it to <a href="http://youtube.com">YouTube</a>, and submit it!</p>
  
  <h2>Step 3</h2>
  
  
  <p>Use the form at the right to tell us a tiny bit about yourself, upload your photo, video or text and give us a brief description if you’d like. From there, our trained oompa loompas will lovingly place your submission on an interactive atlas of Bellingham that employs the fine product Google Maps (wink-wink, nudge-nudge) for the perusing pleasure of our favorite search behemoth and anyone else who visits this site.</p>

  <!-- <p>Stumped? Visit our <%= link_to 'Wish List', '/wish-list' %> of things we'd love you to highlight on the atlas.</p> -->
  <p>Stumped? We'll be posting a wish list soon.</p>

  
  <!-- <%= session[:submission_ids].inspect %> -->
  
</div>
<div class="right">
  <h2>Submit An Entry</h2>
<% semantic_form_for @submission, :html => { :multipart => true } do |f| %>
  <% f.inputs :title => :you do %>
    <%= f.input :name %>
    <%= f.input :email %>
  <% end %>
  


  <fieldset>
    <legend><%=t :'formtastic.titles.location' %></legend>
  	<ul class="candybar">
  		<li class="first"><a href="#" class="address">Address</a></li>
  		<li class="last"><a href="#" class="latlng">Lat/Long</a></li>
  	</ul>

    <% f.inputs :id => 'location_latlng' do %>
      <%= f.input :lat, :required => true %>
      <%= f.input :lng, :required => true %>
    <% end %>
  
    <% f.inputs :id => 'location_address' do %>
      <%= f.input :address, :required => true %>
    <% end %>
  </fieldset>

  <fieldset>
    <legend><%=t :'formtastic.titles.media' %></legend>

  	<ul class="candybar">
  		<li class="first"><a href="#" class="photo">Photo</a></li>
  		<li><a href="#" class="video">Video</a></li>
  		<li class="last"><a href="#" class="none">None</a></li>
  	</ul>
  
    <% f.inputs :id => 'media_photo' do %>
      <%= f.input :photo %>
    <% end %>
  
    <% f.inputs :id => 'media_video' do %>
      <%= f.input :video_url %>
    <% end %>

  	<div id="media_none">&nbsp;</div>
  </fieldset>
  
  <% f.inputs do %>
    <%= f.input :title %>
    <%= f.input :text %>
  <% end %>
    
  <%= f.buttons :commit %>
<% end %>
</div>